Package org.security.crypt.a9cipher

This package contains classes to test commonly used cryptography algorithms.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AES
    A wrapper around the RijndaelCipher class that lets it be used as AESCipher as well.
    CipherMain
    Main class to implement algorithms.
    DES
    The textbook being used gave this example:
    Plaintext: 02468aceeca86420
    Key: 0f1571c947d9e859
    Ciphertext: da02ce3a89ecac3b
    RC4  
    Rijndael

    Ciphertext: ff0b844a0853bf7c6934ab4364148fb9
